<!--<h4>Top of the Stone.</h4>-->

<!--<h4>Left.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>sakava
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>rṣa</unclear>ma
<lb n="3-5"/><ce>worn out</ce>
</p>

<!--<h4>Right</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="6"/>dakāḷa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>daṣṭami
<lb n="8"/>Adi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>varada
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ndu
</p>

<!--<h4>First Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="11"/><unclear>sva</unclear>sti śrī kannaradēva prithuvīrājyaṅgeyye banavāsi<unclear>dē</unclear>
<lb n="12" break="no"/><unclear>saṁ</unclear> kaliviṭṭanuṁ bavasiga <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> yu nāḍāḷe cellapa<unclear>yya</unclear>
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="13"/>sēnemallara mallapaṁ naḻgāmuṇḍugeyye hāvari<unclear>yūra</unclear>
<lb n="14"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> tuṟugoḷe sattu svarggālayakke sanda <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> [O]ḍane parida
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="15"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> nnāgayyaṁ kaḍu
<lb n="16"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> rkkaḷoḷne <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

